description: You see the Paradise Cups mobile trucks everywhere serving South Florida with delightful treats. Paradise Cups are made with the softest snow, infused with one of a kind flavors and topped with gourmet treats. Paradise Cups are handcrafted on their food trucks and each one is made to order. Paradise Cups Snow Creams are deliciously light creamy soft, fluffy snow. Their snow creams are made with the softest snow, infused with one of a kind flavors and topped with gourmet treats. They also hand craft Authentic Hawaiian Shave Ice. Their delicious gourmet creations include Chocolate Madness, Banana Split, Key Lime Pie, Dudley, Lemon Meringue Pie, Reese's, Almond Joy, Root Beer Float, Strawberry Shortcake and many more.Check them out today!
name: Paradise Cups
